taxon="Lemma"></fr:ref> respectively. In the inductive step, we assume that <fr:tex>s\colon  B\to  A</fr:tex> exhibits <fr:tex>B</fr:tex> as a <fr:link
href="erct-0025.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-0025">retract</fr:link> of <fr:tex>A</fr:tex> and that for each <fr:tex>x,y:A</fr:tex> the identification type <fr:tex>x=_Ay</fr:tex> is <fr:link
