style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex>n+1</fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> to show that for all <fr:tex>u,v:B</fr:tex> the identification type <fr:tex>u=_Bv</fr:tex> is likewise <fr:link
href="erct-001G.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-001G"><html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex>n+1</fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link>. The result follows from our assumption and the fact that <fr:tex>u=_Bv</fr:tex> is (by <fr:ref
