  <fr:li>a type is <fr:em><fr:strong><html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex>-1</fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:strong></fr:em> when it is a <fr:link
